data.description: Welcome to Haymount's charming blend of history and modern comfort. This Home, with 3 bedrooms (potential for 5), a formal dining room, and cozy living spaces, exudes warmth and versatility. The sunroom downstairs is ideal for hobbies or basking in natural light. Upstairs, the Owner's Bedroom is a private retreat with two closets and an attached sitting room. Two additional bedrooms offer convenience and privacy. The basement and detached double garage provide practical storage solutions and creative possibilities. Outside, a private oasis awaits with an ornate fire pit area surrounded by lush gardens—a perfect setting for entertaining or quiet moments. The kitchen, with ample cabinets, counter space, and modern appliances, is a culinary haven seamlessly connected to your backyard retreat. This Haymount gem tells a story of timeless elegance and contemporary convenience. Come make lasting memories in this unique blend of history and modern living.
